3345 
3346 void SchedulerU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
3347 {
3348  if (!exist) return;
3349  double ROB_duty_cycle;
3350 // ROB_duty_cycle = ((coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle + coredynp.num_muls>0?coredynp.MUL_duty_cycle:0
3351 // + coredynp.num_fpus>0?coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle:0))*1.1<1 ? (coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle + coredynp.num_muls>0?coredynp.MUL_duty_cycle:0
3352 // + coredynp.num_fpus>0?coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle:0)*1.1:1;
3353  ROB_duty_cycle = 1;
3354  //init stats
3355  if (is_tdp)
3356  {
3357  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
3358  {
3359  int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_search_ports;
3360  int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
3361  int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;
3362  int_inst_window->tdp_stats = int_inst_window->stats_t;
3363  fp_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access = fp_inst_window->l_ip.num_rd_ports*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
3364  fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access = fp_inst_window->l_ip.num_wr_ports*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
3365  fp_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = fp_inst_window->l_ip.num_search_ports*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
3366  fp_inst_window->tdp_stats = fp_inst_window->stats_t;
3367 
3368  if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
3369  {
3370  ROB->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.commitW*coredynp.num_pipelines*ROB_duty_cycle;
3371  ROB->stats_t.writeAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines*ROB_duty_cycle;
3372  ROB->tdp_stats = ROB->stats_t;
3373 
3374  /*
3375  * When inst commits, ROB must be read.
3376  * Because for Physcial register based cores, physical register tag in ROB
3377  * need to be read out and write into RRAT/CAM based RAT.
3378  * For RS based cores, register content that stored in ROB must be
3379  * read out and stored in architectural registers.
3380  *
3381  * if no-register is involved, the ROB read out operation when instruction commits can be ignored.
3382  * assuming 20% insts. belong this type.
3383  * TODO: ROB duty_cycle need to be revisited
3384  */
3385  }
3386 
3387  }
3388  else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
3389  {
3390  int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_search_ports;
3391  int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;//int_inst_window->l_ip.num_wr_ports;
3392  int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = coredynp.issueW*coredynp.num_pipelines;
3393  int_inst_window->tdp_stats = int_inst_window->stats_t;
3394  }
3395 
3396  }
3397  else
3398  {//rtp
3399  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
3400  {
3401  int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].inst_window_reads;
3402  int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].inst_window_writes;
3403  int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].inst_window_wakeup_accesses;
3404  int_inst_window->rtp_stats = int_inst_window->stats_t;
3405  fp_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_inst_window_reads;
3406  fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_inst_window_writes;
3407  fp_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_inst_window_wakeup_accesses;
3408  fp_inst_window->rtp_stats = fp_inst_window->stats_t;
3409 
3410  if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
3411  {
3412 
3413  ROB->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_reads;
3414  ROB->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_writes;
3415  /* ROB need to be updated in RS based OOO when new values are produced,
3416  * this update may happen before the commit stage when ROB entry is released
3417  * 1. ROB write at instruction inserted in
3418  * 2. ROB write as results produced (for RS based OOO only)
3419  * 3. ROB read as instruction committed. For RS based OOO, data values are read out and sent to ARF
3420  * For Physical reg based OOO, no data stored in ROB, but register tags need to be
3421  * read out and used to set the RRAT and to recycle the register tag to free list buffer
3422  */
3423  ROB->rtp_stats = ROB->stats_t;
3424  }
3425 
3426  }
3427  else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
3428  {
3429  int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions + XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions;
3430  int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions + XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions;
3431  int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access = 2*(XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_instructions + XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_instructions);
3432  int_inst_window->rtp_stats = int_inst_window->stats_t;
3433  }
3434  }
3435 
3436  //computation engine
3437  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
3438  {
3439  int_inst_window->power_t.reset();
3440  fp_inst_window->power_t.reset();
3441 
3442  /* each instruction needs to write to scheduler, read out when all resources and source operands are ready
3443  * two search ops with one for each source operand
3444  *
3445  */
3446  int_inst_window->power_t.readOp.dynamic += int_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access
3447  + int_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access
3448  + int_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access
3449  + int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access * instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic;
3450 
3451  fp_inst_window->power_t.readOp.dynamic += fp_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * fp_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access
3452  + fp_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * fp_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access
3453  + fp_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access
3454  + fp_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access * instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic;
3455 
3456  if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
3457  {
3458  ROB->power_t.reset();
3459  ROB->power_t.readOp.dynamic += ROB->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic*ROB->stats_t.readAc.access +
3460  ROB->stats_t.writeAc.access*ROB->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
3461  }
3462 
3463 
3464 
3465 
3466  }
3467  else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
3468  {
3469  int_inst_window->power_t.reset();
3470  int_inst_window->power_t.readOp.dynamic += int_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access
3471  + int_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.searchAc.access
3472  + int_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access
3473  + int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access * instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic;
3474  }
3475 
3476  //assign values
3477  if (is_tdp)
3478  {
3479  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
3480  {
3481  int_inst_window->power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
3482  fp_inst_window->power = fp_inst_window->power_t + (fp_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
3483  power = power + int_inst_window->power + fp_inst_window->power;
3484  if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
3485  {
3486  ROB->power = ROB->power_t + ROB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
3487  power = power + ROB->power;
3488  }
3489 
3490  }
3491  else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
3492  {
3493  // set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width,1, 1, 1);
3494  int_inst_window->power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
3495  power = power + int_inst_window->power;
3496  }
3497 
3498  }
3499  else
3500  {//rtp
3501  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
3502  {
3503  int_inst_window->rt_power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
3504  fp_inst_window->rt_power = fp_inst_window->power_t + (fp_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
3505  rt_power = rt_power + int_inst_window->rt_power + fp_inst_window->rt_power;
3506  if (XML->sys.core[ithCore].ROB_size >0)
3507  {
3508  ROB->rt_power = ROB->power_t + ROB->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
3509  rt_power = rt_power + ROB->rt_power;
3510  }
3511 
3512  }
3513  else if (coredynp.multithreaded)
3514  {
3515  // set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width,1, 1, 1);
3516  int_inst_window->rt_power = int_inst_window->power_t + (int_inst_window->local_result.power +instruction_selection->power) *pppm_lkg;
3517  rt_power = rt_power + int_inst_window->rt_power;
3518  }
3519  }
3520 // set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width,1, 1, 1);
3521 // cout<<"Scheduler power="<<power.readOp.dynamic<<"leakage="<<power.readOp.leakage<<endl;
3522 // cout<<"IW="<<int_inst_window->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.readAc.access +
3523 // + int_inst_window->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic * int_inst_window->stats_t.writeAc.access<<"leakage="<<int_inst_window->local_result.power.readOp.leakage<<endl;
3524 // cout<<"selection"<<instruction_selection->power.readOp.dynamic<<"leakage"<<instruction_selection->power.readOp.leakage<<endl;
3525 }

3606 void LoadStoreU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
3607 {

3609 
3610  executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
3611 
3612  //RF crossbar power (Syed)
3613  xbar_shared->compute_power();
3614 
3615  if (is_tdp)
3616  {
3617 
3618  //init stats for Peak
3619  // added by Jingwen
3620  sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.access = 0.67*sharedmemory.caches->l_ip.num_rw_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;
3621  sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss = 0;
3622  sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.hit = sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.access - sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.readAc.miss;
3623  sharedmemory.caches->stats_t.writeAc.access = 0.33*sharedmemory.caches->l_ip.num_rw_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;

4065 // dcache.wbb->local_result.power)*pppm_lkg;
4066  rt_power.reset();
4067  sharedmemory.rt_power.reset(); //Jingwen
4068  tcache.rt_power.reset();
4069  ccache.rt_power.reset();
4070  dcache.rt_power.reset();
4071  LSQ->rt_power.reset();
4072 
4073 
4074  sharedmemory.rt_power = sharedmemory.power_t + (sharedmemory.caches->local_result.power +
4075  sharedmemory.missb->local_result.power +
4076  sharedmemory.ifb->local_result.power +
4077  sharedmemory.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
4078 
4079  if (cache_p==Write_back)
4080  {
4081  sharedmemory.rt_power = sharedmemory.rt_power + sharedmemory.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
4082  }
4083 
4084  dcache.rt_power = dcache.power_t + (dcache.caches->local_result.power +
4085  dcache.missb->local_result.power +
4086  dcache.ifb->local_result.power +
4087  dcache.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
4088  if (cache_p==Write_back)
4089  {
4090  dcache.rt_power = dcache.rt_power + dcache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
4091  }
4092 
4093  ccache.rt_power = ccache.power_t + (ccache.caches->local_result.power +
4094  ccache.missb->local_result.power +
4095  ccache.ifb->local_result.power +
4096  ccache.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
4097  if (cache_p==Write_back)
4098  {
4099  ccache.rt_power = ccache.rt_power + ccache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
4100  }
4101 
4102  tcache.rt_power = tcache.power_t + (tcache.caches->local_result.power +
4103  tcache.missb->local_result.power +
4104  tcache.ifb->local_result.power +
4105  tcache.prefetchb->local_result.power )*pppm_lkg;
4106  if (cache_p==Write_back)
4107  {
4108  tcache.rt_power = tcache.rt_power + tcache.wbb->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
4109  }
4110 
4111 
4112 
4113  LSQ->rt_power = LSQ->power_t + LSQ->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4114  LSQ->rt_power.reset();
4115  rt_power = rt_power + dcache.rt_power + LSQ->rt_power + sharedmemory.rt_power + ccache.rt_power + tcache.rt_power;
4116 
4117  if ((coredynp.core_ty==OOO) && (XML->sys.core[ithCore].load_buffer_size >0))
4118  {
4119  LoadQ->rt_power = LoadQ->power_t + LoadQ->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4120  rt_power = rt_power + LoadQ->rt_power;
4121  }
4122  }
4123 }

4251 void MemManU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
4252 {
4253 
4254  if (!exist) return;
4255  if (is_tdp)
4256  {
4257  //init stats for Peak
4258  itlb->stats_t.readAc.access = itlb->l_ip.num_search_ports;
4259  itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss = 0;
4260  itlb->stats_t.readAc.hit = itlb->stats_t.readAc.access - itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
4261  itlb->tdp_stats = itlb->stats_t;
4262 
4263  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access = dtlb->l_ip.num_search_ports*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle;
4264  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss = 0;
4265  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.hit = dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access - dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
4266  dtlb->tdp_stats = dtlb->stats_t;
4267  }
4268  else
4269  {
4270  //init stats for Runtime Dynamic (RTP)
4271  itlb->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].itlb.total_accesses;
4272  itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss = XML->sys.core[ithCore].itlb.total_misses;
4273  itlb->stats_t.readAc.hit = itlb->stats_t.readAc.access - itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
4274  itlb->rtp_stats = itlb->stats_t;
4275 
4276  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].dtlb.total_accesses;
4277  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss = XML->sys.core[ithCore].dtlb.total_misses;
4278  dtlb->stats_t.readAc.hit = dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access - dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss;
4279  dtlb->rtp_stats = dtlb->stats_t;
4280  }
4281 
4282  itlb->power_t.reset();
4283  dtlb->power_t.reset();
4284  itlb->power_t.readOp.dynamic += itlb->stats_t.readAc.access*itlb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic//FA spent most power in tag, so use total access not hits
4285  +itlb->stats_t.readAc.miss*itlb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
4286  dtlb->power_t.readOp.dynamic += dtlb->stats_t.readAc.access*dtlb->local_result.power.searchOp.dynamic//FA spent most power in tag, so use total access not hits
4287  +dtlb->stats_t.readAc.miss*dtlb->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic;
4288 
4289  if (is_tdp)
4290  {
4291  itlb->power = itlb->power_t + itlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4292  dtlb->power = dtlb->power_t + dtlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4293  power = power + itlb->power + dtlb->power;
4294  }
4295  else
4296  {
4297  itlb->rt_power = itlb->power_t + itlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4298  dtlb->rt_power = dtlb->power_t + dtlb->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4299  rt_power = rt_power + itlb->rt_power + dtlb->rt_power;
4300  }
4301 
4302 }

4344 
4345 void RegFU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
4346 {
4347 /*
4348  * Architecture RF and physical RF cannot be present at the same time.
4349  * Therefore, the RF stats can only refer to either ARF or PRF;
4350  * And the same stats can be used for both.
4351  */
4352  if (!exist) return;
4353 
4354  executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
4355  //RF crossbar power (Syed Gilani)
4356  xbar_rfu->compute_power();
4357 
4358 
4359  //Arbiter power
4360  arbiter_rfu->compute_power();
4361 
4362  if (is_tdp)
4363  {
4364  //RF power -- modified by Syed
4365  //init stats for Peak
4366 
4367  IRF->stats_t.readAc.access = 4;
4368  IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = 4;
4369  IRF->tdp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
4370 
4371  IRF->stats_t.readAc.access = 2;
4372  IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = 1;
4373  IRF->tdp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
4374 
4375 
4376  OPC->stats_t.readAc.access = 32;
4377  OPC->stats_t.writeAc.access = 32;
4378  OPC->tdp_stats = OPC->stats_t;
4379 
4380  //Commented by Syed (GPUs have a single RF which we model by IRF)
4381  //FRF->stats_t.readAc.access = FRF->l_ip.num_rd_ports*coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle*1.05*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
4382  //FRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = FRF->l_ip.num_wr_ports*coredynp.FPU_duty_cycle*1.05*coredynp.num_fp_pipelines;
4383  //FRF->tdp_stats = FRF->stats_t;
4384  if (coredynp.regWindowing)
4385  {
4386  RFWIN->stats_t.readAc.access = 0;//0.5*RFWIN->l_ip.num_rw_ports;
4387  RFWIN->stats_t.writeAc.access = 0;//0.5*RFWIN->l_ip.num_rw_ports;
4388  RFWIN->tdp_stats = RFWIN->stats_t;
4389  }
4390  } /* if (is_tdp) */
4391  else
4392  {
4393  //init stats for Runtime Dynamic (RTP)
4394  //in Tesla each RF operand accesses 2 banks, so multiply acceses by 2
4395  // (read and write energies of reg_file are per bank)(Tesla) : Syed
4396  // Also, for a SIMD width of 8 and warp size of 32 threads, 4 accesses
4397  // (each accessing 2 banks) need to be performed per operand
4398 if (XML->sys.architecture==1){
4399  IRF->stats_t.readAc.access = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/32)*(4*2);
4400  IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_writes/32)*(4*2);
4401 } else {
4402  IRF->stats_t.readAc.access = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/32)*(2*4);
4403  IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_writes/32)*(2*4);
4404 }
4405  IRF->rtp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
4406 
4407  OPC->stats_t.readAc.access = (XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads)/*/1.5*/+XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands;
4408  OPC->stats_t.writeAc.access = 0;
4409  OPC->rtp_stats = OPC->stats_t;
4410 
4411  //cout<< "IRF read energy: "<< IRF->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic<<endl;
4412  //cout<< "IRF write energy: "<< IRF->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic<<endl;
4413  //FRF->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].float_regfile_reads;
4414  //FRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].float_regfile_writes;
4415  //FRF->rtp_stats = FRF->stats_t;
4416  if (coredynp.regWindowing)
4417  {
4418  RFWIN->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
4419  RFWIN->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
4420  RFWIN->rtp_stats = RFWIN->stats_t;
4421 
4422  IRF->stats_t.readAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads +
4423  XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
4424  IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access = XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_writes +
4425  XML->sys.core[ithCore].function_calls*16;
4426  IRF->rtp_stats = IRF->stats_t;
4427 
4428  }
4429  }
4430  IRF->power_t.reset();
4431  FRF->power_t.reset();
4432  OPC->power_t.reset();
4433  //IRF->power_t = IRF->power_t + IRF->local_result.power;// + xbar_rfu->power + arbiter_rfu->power;
4434 
4435 
4436 
4437  IRF->power_t.readOp.dynamic = (IRF->stats_t.readAc.access*IRF->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic
4438  +IRF->stats_t.writeAc.access*IRF->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
4439  OPC->power_t.readOp.dynamic = (OPC->stats_t.readAc.access*OPC->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic);
4440 
4441  if (coredynp.regWindowing)
4442  {
4443  RFWIN->power_t.reset();
4444  RFWIN->power_t.readOp.dynamic += (RFWIN->stats_t.readAc.access*RFWIN->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic +
4445  RFWIN->stats_t.writeAc.access*RFWIN->local_result.power.writeOp.dynamic);
4446  }
4447 
4448  if (is_tdp)
4449  {
4450 
4451  //cout<<"pre: IRF_power_t: "<<IRF->power.readOp.dynamic<<" ("<<IRF->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate<<") "<<" IRF_localresult: "<<
4452  // IRF->local_result.power.readOp.dynamic<<endl;
4453  //Syed: removed the multiplication of power by hardware threads
4454  //since the one IRF is shared by all threads in GPUs
4455 
4456  //FRF->power = FRF->power_t + FRF->local_result.power *coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;
4457 
4458  double pppm_lkg_banks[4];
4459  set_pppm(pppm_lkg_banks, 0,XML->sys.core[ithCore].collector_units,XML->sys.core[ithCore].collector_units );
4460  IRF->power = (IRF->power_t) + IRF->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
4461  IRF->power.readOp.dynamic=IRF->power_t.readOp.dynamic*1;
4462  OPC->power = (OPC->power_t) + OPC->local_result.power *pppm_lkg_banks;
4463  OPC->power.readOp.dynamic=OPC->power_t.readOp.dynamic*1;
4464 
4465 
4466  power = power + (IRF->power+OPC->power);
4467 
4468 
4469  if (coredynp.regWindowing)
4470  {
4471  RFWIN->power = RFWIN->power_t + RFWIN->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4472  power = power + RFWIN->power;
4473  }
4474  } /* if (is_tdp) */
4475  else
4476  {
4477  //Removed *coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread since all hardware threads shared the same IRF
4478  IRF->rt_power = IRF->power_t + IRF->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;/* *coredynp.pppm_lkg_multhread;*/
4479  OPC->rt_power = OPC->power_t + OPC->local_result.power*pppm_lkg;
4480 if(XML->sys.architecture==1){
4481  //Each warp operand accesses the crossbar
4482  xbar_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic=((XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/(32))+(XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands/(32)))*xbar_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic;
4483 } else {
4484  xbar_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic=((XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/(32))+(XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands/(32)))*xbar_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic;
4485 }
4486  arbiter_rfu->rt_power.readOp.dynamic=((XML->sys.core[ithCore].int_regfile_reads/(32))+(XML->sys.core[ithCore].non_rf_operands/(32)))*arbiter_rfu->power.readOp.dynamic;
4487 
4488 
4489  rt_power = rt_power + (IRF->power_t /*+ FRF->power_t*/+xbar_rfu->rt_power+arbiter_rfu->rt_power+OPC->power_t);
4490  if (coredynp.regWindowing)
4491  {
4492  RFWIN->rt_power = RFWIN->power_t + RFWIN->local_result.power *pppm_lkg;
4493  rt_power = rt_power + RFWIN->rt_power;
4494  }
4495  }
4496 }

4576 void EXECU::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
4577 {
4578  if (!exist) return;
4579  //Syed
4580  double pppm_t[4] = {1,1,1,1};
4581  double pppm_freqScaling[4] = {rf_fu_clockRate/clockRate,1,1,1};
4582  executionTime=XML->sys.total_cycles/(XML->sys.target_core_clockrate*1e6);//Syed
4583 
4584 
4585 // rfu->power.reset();
4586  rfu->rt_power.reset();
4587 // scheu->power.reset();
4588  scheu->rt_power.reset();
4589 // exeu->power.reset();
4590  exeu->rt_power.reset();
4591 
4592  rfu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4593  scheu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4594  exeu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4595  if (coredynp.num_fpus >0)
4596  {
4597  fp_u->rt_power.reset();
4598  fp_u->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4599  }
4600  if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
4601  {
4602  mul->rt_power.reset();
4603  mul->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4604  }
4605  bypass.rt_power.reset();
4606 
4607  if (is_tdp)
4608  {
4609  set_pppm(pppm_t, 2*coredynp.ALU_cdb_duty_cycle, 2, 2, 2*coredynp.ALU_cdb_duty_cycle);//2 means two source operands needs to be passed for each int instruction.
4610  //bypass.power = bypass.power + intTagBypass->power*pppm_t + int_bypass->power*pppm_t;
4611  if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
4612  {
4613  set_pppm(pppm_t, 2*coredynp.MUL_cdb_duty_cycle, 2, 2, 2*coredynp.MUL_cdb_duty_cycle);//2 means two source operands needs to be passed for each int instruction.
4614  //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
4615  //bypass.power = bypass.power + intTag_mul_Bypass->power*pppm_t + int_mul_bypass->power*pppm_t;
4616  power = power + mul->power*pppm_freqScaling;
4617  }
4618 
4619  if (coredynp.num_fpus>0)
4620  {
4621  set_pppm(pppm_t, 3*coredynp.FPU_cdb_duty_cycle, 3, 3, 3*coredynp.FPU_cdb_duty_cycle);//3 means three source operands needs to be passed for each fp instruction.
4622  //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
4623  //bypass.power = bypass.power + fp_bypass->power*pppm_t + fpTagBypass->power*pppm_t ;
4624  power = power + fp_u->power*pppm_freqScaling;
4625 
4626  }
4627  //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
4628 
4629  power = power + rfu->power*pppm_freqScaling + exeu->power*pppm_freqScaling /*+ bypass.power*/ + scheu->power
4630  ;
4631 
4632 
4633  }
4634  else
4635  {
4636  set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_alu_accesses, 2, 2, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_alu_accesses);
4637  //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + intTagBypass->power*pppm_t;
4638  //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + int_bypass->power*pppm_t;
4639 
4640  if (coredynp.num_muls >0)
4641  {
4642  set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_mul_accesses, 2, 2, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_mul_accesses);//2 means two source operands needs to be passed for each int instruction.
4643  //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + intTag_mul_Bypass->power*pppm_t + int_mul_bypass->power*pppm_t;
4644  rt_power = rt_power + mul->rt_power;
4645  }
4646 
4647  if (coredynp.num_fpus>0)
4648  {
4649  set_pppm(pppm_t, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_fpu_accesses, 3, 3, XML->sys.core[ithCore].cdb_fpu_accesses);
4650  //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + fp_bypass->power*pppm_t;
4651  //bypass.rt_power = bypass.rt_power + fpTagBypass->power*pppm_t;
4652  rt_power = rt_power + fp_u->rt_power;
4653  }
4654  //No conventional bypassing in GPU (Syed)
4655  rt_power = rt_power + rfu->rt_power*pppm_freqScaling + exeu->rt_power*pppm_freqScaling + /*bypass.rt_power +*/ scheu->rt_power;
4656  }
4657 }

4731 //Jingwen
4732 void Core::compute()
4733 {
4734  //power_point_product_masks
4735  double pppm_t[4] = {1,1,1,1};
4736  double rtp_pipeline_coe;
4737  double num_units = 4.0;
4738  Pipeline_energy=0;
4739 
4740  //Set pipeline duty cycle for this inteval
4741  coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle=XML->sys.core[ithCore].pipeline_duty_cycle;
4742  rt_power.reset();
4743  ifu->rt_power.reset();
4744  lsu->rt_power.reset();
4745  mmu->rt_power.reset();
4746  exu->rt_power.reset();
4747 
4748 
4749  ifu->computeEnergy(false);
4750  lsu->computeEnergy(false);
4751  mmu->computeEnergy(false);
4752  exu->computeEnergy(false);
4753 
4754 
4755  if (XML->sys.homogeneous_cores==1)
4756  {
4757  rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * XML->sys.total_cycles * XML->sys.number_of_cores;
4758  }
4759  else
4760  {
4761 
4762  rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * coredynp.total_cycles;
4763  //Jingwen
4764  if (coredynp.total_cycles != XML->sys.total_cycles)
4765  {
4766  cout << "total cycle not match!" << endl;
4767  exit(1);
4768  }
4769  }
4770 
4771  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4772 
4773  if (ifu->exist)
4774  {
4775  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4776  ifu->rt_power = ifu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4777  rt_power = rt_power + ifu->rt_power ;
4778  }
4779 
4780  if (lsu->exist)
4781  {
4782  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4783  lsu->rt_power = lsu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4784  rt_power = rt_power + lsu->rt_power;
4785  }
4786  if (exu->exist)
4787  {
4788  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4789  exu->rt_power = exu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4790  rt_power = rt_power + exu->rt_power;
4791  }
4792  if (mmu->exist)
4793  {
4794  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4795  mmu->rt_power = mmu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4796  rt_power = rt_power + mmu->rt_power ;
4797  }
4798 
4799  rt_power = rt_power + undiffCore->power;
4800 
4801 
4802  if (XML->sys.Private_L2)
4803  {
4804 
4805  l2cache->computeEnergy(false);
4806  rt_power = rt_power + l2cache->rt_power;
4807  }
4808 
4809  IdleCoreEnergy=XML->sys.num_idle_cores * XML->sys.idle_core_power* executionTime;
4810 
4811  rt_power.readOp.dynamic += IdleCoreEnergy;
4812 
4813 }

4818 void Core::computeEnergy(bool is_tdp)
4819 {
4820  //power_point_product_masks
4821  double pppm_t[4] = {1,1,1,1};
4822  double rtp_pipeline_coe;
4823  double num_units = 4.0;
4824  Pipeline_energy=0;
4825 
4826  if (XML->sys.homogeneous_cores==1)
4827  {
4828  rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * XML->sys.total_cycles * XML->sys.number_of_cores;
4829  }
4830  else
4831  {
4832  rtp_pipeline_coe = coredynp.pipeline_duty_cycle * coredynp.total_cycles;
4833  }
4834 
4835 
4836  if (is_tdp)
4837  {
4838  ifu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4839  lsu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4840  mmu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4841  exu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4842 
4843  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
4844  {
4845  num_units = 5.0;
4846  rnu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4847  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4848  if (rnu->exist)
4849  {
4850  rnu->power = rnu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4851  power = power + rnu->power;
4852  }
4853  }
4854 
4855  if (ifu->exist)
4856  {
4857  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4858  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.IFU_duty_cycle, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4859 // cout << "IFU = " << ifu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4860  ifu->power = ifu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4861 // cout << "IFU = " << ifu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4862 // cout << "1/4 pipe = " << corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate/num_units << " W" << endl;
4863  power = power + ifu->power;
4864 // cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4865  }
4866  if (lsu->exist)
4867  {
4868  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4869  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4870  lsu->power = lsu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4871 // cout << "LSU = " << lsu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4872  power = power + lsu->power;
4873 // cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4874  }
4875  if (exu->exist)
4876  {
4877  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4878  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4879  //cout<<"ExPowerScalingFactor:"<<coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*coredynp.ALU_duty_cycle<<endl;
4880  exu->power = exu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4881 // cout << "EXE = " << exu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4882  power = power + exu->power;
4883 // cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4884  }
4885  if (mmu->exist)
4886  {
4887  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4888  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units*(0.5+0.5*coredynp.LSU_duty_cycle), coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4889  mmu->power = mmu->power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4890 // cout << "MMU = " << mmu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4891  power = power + mmu->power;
4892 // cout << "core = " << power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4893  }
4894 
4895  power = power + undiffCore->power;
4896 
4897  if (XML->sys.Private_L2)
4898  {
4899 
4900  l2cache->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4901  set_pppm(pppm_t,l2cache->cachep.clockRate/clockRate, 1,1,1);
4902  //l2cache->power = l2cache->power*pppm_t;
4903  power = power + l2cache->power*pppm_t;
4904  }
4905 
4906  }
4907  else
4908  {
4909  rt_power.reset();
4910 
4911 
4912 
4913 
4914  ifu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4915  lsu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4916  mmu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4917  exu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4918  if (coredynp.core_ty==OOO)
4919  {
4920  num_units = 5.0;
4921  rnu->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4922  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4923  if (rnu->exist)
4924  {
4925  rnu->rt_power = rnu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4926 
4927  rt_power = rt_power + rnu->rt_power;
4928  }
4929  }
4930  else
4931  {
4932 
4933  set_pppm(pppm_t, coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units, coredynp.num_pipelines/num_units);
4934  }
4935 
4936  if (ifu->exist)
4937  {
4938  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4939  ifu->rt_power = ifu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4940  rt_power = rt_power + ifu->rt_power ;
4941  }
4942  if (lsu->exist)
4943  {
4944  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4945  lsu->rt_power = lsu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4946  rt_power = rt_power + lsu->rt_power;
4947  }
4948  if (exu->exist)
4949  {
4950  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4951  exu->rt_power = exu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4952  rt_power = rt_power + exu->rt_power;
4953  }
4954  if (mmu->exist)
4955  {
4956  Pipeline_energy+=corepipe->power.readOp.dynamic* (coredynp.num_pipelines*rtp_pipeline_coe/num_units);
4957  mmu->rt_power = mmu->rt_power + corepipe->power*pppm_t;
4958  rt_power = rt_power + mmu->rt_power ;
4959  }
4960 
4961  rt_power = rt_power + undiffCore->power;
4962 // cout << "EXE = " << exu->power.readOp.dynamic*clockRate << " W" << endl;
4963  if (XML->sys.Private_L2)
4964  {
4965  l2cache->computeEnergy(is_tdp);
4966  //set_pppm(pppm_t,1/l2cache->cachep.executionTime, 1,1,1);
4967  //l2cache->rt_power = l2cache->rt_power*pppm_t;
4968  rt_power = rt_power + l2cache->rt_power;
4969  }
4970 
4971  }
4972 
4973 }

5211 void Core::set_core_param()
5212 {
5213  coredynp.opt_local = XML->sys.core[ithCore].opt_local;
5214  coredynp.x86 = XML->sys.core[ithCore].x86;
5215  coredynp.Embedded = XML->sys.Embedded;
5216  coredynp.core_ty = (enum Core_type)XML->sys.core[ithCore].machine_type;
5217  coredynp.rm_ty = (enum Renaming_type)XML->sys.core[ithCore].rename_scheme;
5218  coredynp.fetchW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fetch_width;
5219  coredynp.decodeW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].decode_width;
5220  coredynp.issueW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].issue_width;
5221  coredynp.peak_issueW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].peak_issue_width;
5222  coredynp.commitW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].commit_width;
5223  coredynp.peak_commitW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].peak_issue_width;
5224  coredynp.predictionW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].prediction_width;
5225  coredynp.fp_issueW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_issue_width;
5226  coredynp.fp_decodeW = XML->sys.core[ithCore].fp_issue_width;
5227  coredynp.num_alus = XML->sys.core[ithCore].ALU_per_core;
5228  coredynp.num_fpus = XML->sys.core[ithCore].FPU_per_core;
5229  coredynp.num_muls = XML->sys.core[ithCore].MUL_per_core;
5230 
5231 
5232  coredynp.num_hthreads = XML->sys.core[ithCore].number_hardware_threads;
5233  coredynp.multithreaded = coredynp.num_hthreads>1? true:false;
5234  coredynp.instruction_length = XML->sys.core[ithCore].instruction_length;
5235  coredynp.pc_width = XML->sys.virtual_address_width;
5236 
5237  coredynp.opcode_length = XML->sys.core[ithCore].opcode_width;
5238  coredynp.micro_opcode_length = XML->sys.core[ithCore].micro_opcode_width;
5239  coredynp.num_pipelines = XML->sys.core[ithCore].pipelines_per_core[0];
5240  coredynp.pipeline_stages = XML->sys.core[ithCore].pipeline_depth[0];
5241  coredynp.num_fp_pipelines = XML->sys.core[ithCore].pipelines_per_core[1];
5242  coredynp.fp_pipeline_stages = XML->sys.core[ithCore].pipeline_depth[1];
5243  coredynp.int_data_width = int(ceil(XML->sys.machine_bits/32.0))*32;
5244  coredynp.fp_data_width = coredynp.int_data_width;
5245  coredynp.v_address_width = XML->sys.virtual_address_width;
5246  coredynp.p_address_width = XML->sys.physical_address_width;
5247 
5248  coredynp.scheu_ty = (enum Scheduler_type)XML->sys.core[ithCore].instruction_window_scheme;
5249  coredynp.arch_ireg_width = int(ceil(log2(XML->sys.core[ithCore].archi_Regs_IRF_size)));
